<mjml>
  <mj-head>
    <mj-preview>You're invited to join {{.OrganizationName}} on PoeticMetric, gain valuable insights, collaborate with your team, and access
      all features with our privacy-first analytics platform. Click to join now!
    </mj-preview>

    <mj-attributes>
      <mj-button
          background-color="#3182CE"
          border-radius="6px"
          font-family="-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif"
          font-size="16px"
          font-weight="600"
      />

      <mj-text
          color="#2D3748"
          font-family="-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif"
          font-size="16px"
          font-weight="400"
          line-height="24px"
          padding-left="40px"
          padding-right="40px"
      />
    </mj-attributes>

    <mj-style inline="inline">
      a {
        font-weight: 700;
        text-decoration: none;
        color: #3182CE;
      }
    </mj-style>
  </mj-head>

  <mj-body background-color="#F7FAFC">
    <mj-section>
      <mj-column>
        <mj-spacer height="20px" />
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <mj-section background-color="#EBF8FF" border-radius="8px 8px 0 0">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-image
            width="200px"
            src="https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/698079/139349672-47706255-455f-4859-955c-2d1e927add90.png"
            align="center"
            alt="PoeticMetric Logo"
            href="{{.FrontendBaseUrl}}"
        />
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <mj-section background-color="#ffffff" border-radius="0 0 6px 6px">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-text>
          <p>Greetings,</p>

          <p>
            We are excited to invite you to join <strong>{{.OrganizationName}}</strong> on PoeticMetric, our privacy-first,
            regulation-compliant, and blazingly fast analytics platform.
          </p>

          <p>
            As a member of the <strong>{{.OrganizationName}}</strong> team, you will have access to all the features and benefits of
            PoeticMetric, including:
          </p>

          <ul>
            <li><strong>Gain valuable insights</strong> into {{.OrganizationName}}'s website traffic</li>

            <li><strong>Collaborate with the rest of the team</strong> on analyzing data</li>

            <li><strong>Have access to all the features and benefits</strong> of PoeticMetric</li>
          </ul>

          <p>To accept the invitation and join the team, please click on the following link:</p>
        </mj-text>

        <mj-button href="{{.ActivationUrl}}">Accept the invite</mj-button>

        <mj-text>
          <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please don't hesitate to reach out to our support team.</p>

          <p>Cheers,</p>

          <p>The PoeticMetric Team</p>
        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <mj-section padding-top="8px">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-text font-size="12px" align="center">Copyright Â© WebGazer, Inc.</mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
  </mj-body>
</mjml>
